    Page: 42
    Verse: 15
Tags:
  - Cause & Effect
---
The world is a looking glass, and gives back to every man the reflection of
his own face. Frown at it, and it will in turn look sourly upon you; laugh
at it and with it, and it is a jolly, kind companion.
